{"title":"Argonaut adds the Supernaut road and gravel bikes to its permanent range","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/argonaut-supernaut","date":1732197600000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/argonaut-supernaut\">Argonaut adds the Supernaut road and gravel bikes to its permanent range</a></p>\n\n<p>The Argonaut Supernaut was billed as a limited edition when it was launched in 2023, but now Argonaut has added the Supernaut RM3 road and GR3 gravel bike to its permanent bike range.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can buy the Supernaut in 13 different sizes and with fixed specs with premium builds including Argonaut carbon wheels. The Supernaut RM3 is priced at $16,500 and the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/argonaut-supernaut-gr3-review\" target=\"_blank\">Supernaut GR3</a> at $15,900, with a $1,000 deposit. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2>Non-custom option</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"645\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-970x645.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-300x199.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-768x511.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-1536x1021.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-2048x1362.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-750x499.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-1140x758.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-5-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Based in Bend, Oregon, Argonaut specialises in built-to-order custom carbon framesets, when it tunes its carbon lay-up to the rider’s weight and power output. If you won’t fit on one of its stock frame sizes, it says that it will build a template for you. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to Argonaut, it matches the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/bike-frame-stiffness\" target=\"_blank\">frame’s flex</a> to the force generated by the rider, to provide enhanced ride quality, which it says ‘elevates every piece of the rider’s capabilities’.</p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/argonaut-supernaut-gr3-review\">Argonaut Supernaut GR3 review</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/argonaut-rm3-review\">Argonaut RM3 review</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-gravel-bike\">The best gravel bikes 2024 reviewed</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/road-gravel-bike-rim-width\">Road and gravel bike rim width: What’s best and why?</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-road-bike\">Best road bikes 2024 reviewed and rated</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<figure><div></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"644\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-970x644.jpeg\" alt=\"Argonaut Supernaut RM3\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-970x644.jpeg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-300x199.jpeg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-768x510.jpeg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-1536x1021.jpeg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-2048x1361.jpeg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-750x498.jpeg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-1140x757.jpeg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-465x310.jpeg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-620x413.jpeg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supenaut-RM3-350x233.jpeg 350w\" /><figcaption>Argonaut </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Supernaut was a new departure for the brand, as it’s built to a standard <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/how-does-frame-geometry-affect-a-bike\" target=\"_blank\">geometry</a>, with standard carbon lay-up and components. Rather than match the bike to you, the Supernaut is available in 13 sizes, so that Argonaut can match you to the right size frame, choosing component sizes to fine-tune the fit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As with its other bikes, the Supernaut is completely hand-built in Bend, Oregon, using Argonaut’s HPDS moulding process. Argonaut even produces its own tooling for the moulds.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now Argonaut says that it has scheduled 30 production slots for the Supernaut in 2025. The Supernaut will be sold exclusively as a complete build with one colour option: raw carbon with ‘Caribbean Pearl’ accents.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Argonaut Supernaut GR3\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-Supernaut-GR3-4-1-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Argonaut </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There are two Supernaut options, the RM3 road bike and the GR3 gravel bike. We reviewed the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/argonaut-supernaut-gr3-review\" target=\"_blank\">Argonaut Supernaut GR3</a> in February 2024. It’s characterised by a very slack 68.5° head tube angle, which editor Pete Muir found added stability on fast descents.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve not ridden the Supernaut RM3, but deputy editor James Spender has reviewed a non-custom <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/argonaut-rm3-review\" target=\"_blank\">Argonaut RM3</a> (they’re not going to build a custom bike just for <em>Cyclist</em>), which he rated as ‘probably the best road bike you’ll ever ride’, although with the frameset alone costing £5,500, it’s probably the most expensive too.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>New D33 gravel wheelset</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><div></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Argonaut D33 wheelset\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Argonaut-D33-wheelset-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Argonaut</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Argonaut has a new gravel wheelset out as well, which comes fitted to the GR3. Called the D33, it too is hand-built in Bend. As you might expect, it’s 33mm deep, but other spec highlights include a 28mm internal width <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/hookless-rims\" target=\"_blank\">hookless rim</a> with a 375g claimed weight, for a 1,269g claimed wheelset weight. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>That 28mm width is not quite up there with the<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/zipp-303-xplr-wheels\" target=\"_blank\"> Zipp 303 XPLR</a>’s 32mm internal rim width, but Argonaut says that it results in tyres between 40mm and 50mm wide fitting more stably, enhancing traction and compliance and reducing the risk of tyre roll when cornering. It recommends tyres between 35mm and 50mm in width.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The D33 wheels have Carbon-Ti hubs and DT Aerolite straight-pull spokes. They’re priced at $2,800 a set.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Argonaut Supernaut build specs and prices </h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Supernaut RM3</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Groupset Options</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>SRAM Red AXS (with optional Ceramic Speed OSPW upgrade)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shimano Dura Ace Group with Ceramic Speed OSPW</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bottom bracket:</strong> Ceramic Speed T47 BB</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheels:</strong> Argonaut R43 Wheels</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bar/Stem: </strong>Enve Integrated Cockpit (Enve one-piece bar/stem upgrade available)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tyres</strong>: Schwalbe Pro One 28mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Seatpost</strong>: Enve</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Saddle</strong>: Selle Repente Artax GLM Saddle</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Colour</strong>: Raw carbon with Caribbean Pearl accents, high gloss protective coat.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Price</strong>: $16,500</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Supernaut GR3</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Groupset Options:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>SRAM Red XPLR 13-spd (with optional Ceramic Speed OSPW upgrade)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shimano GRX/XTR Group with e13 Helix Cassette and Ceramic Speed OSPW</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bottom bracket:</strong> Ceramic Speed T47 BB</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheels:</strong> New Argonaut D33 Wheels</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bar/Stem: </strong>Enve Integrated Cockpit (Enve one-piece bar/stem upgrade available)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tyres</strong>: Schwalbe G-One R 40mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Seatpost</strong>: Enve</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Saddle</strong>: Selle Repente Artax GLM Saddle</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Colour</strong>: Raw carbon with Caribbean Pearl accents, Cerakote protective coat</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Price</strong>: $15,900</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"351\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-3-970x351.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-3-970x351.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-3-300x109.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-3-768x278.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-3-1536x556.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-3-2048x741.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-3-750x271.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-3-1140x412.jpg 1140w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n    